00:00:10.433 --> 00:00:13.466
and test those popular products on the market.

00:00:13.633 --> 00:00:16.000
But my perspective on skin care products

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.666
may be different from many colleagues.

00:00:18.900 --> 00:00:21.066
Because I majored in biology,

00:00:21.100 --> 00:00:21.433
So,

00:00:21.433 --> 00:00:25.466
I don't like to focus on those chemical terms.

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:27.200
I prefer to think about

00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:30.133
When these ingredients are applied to our faces,

00:00:30.133 --> 00:00:31.633
what will happen to our skin.

00:00:31.733 --> 00:00:33.066
So when making formulas

00:00:33.066 --> 00:00:34.666
and when doing tests,

00:00:34.666 --> 00:00:36.500
I prefer to ask myself

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:39.600
When these ingredients are combined together,

00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:41.000
are really effective

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:43.066
or just for marketing?

00:00:43.100 --> 00:00:45.266
After testing a product,

00:00:45.266 --> 00:00:48.133
really as amazing as its advertisement says?

00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:49.066
These questions

00:00:49.066 --> 00:00:51.466
it sounds like I'm paranoid.

00:00:51.533 --> 00:00:52.700
But as a formulator,

00:00:52.700 --> 00:00:55.600
I must stand on the same side as you.

00:00:55.766 --> 00:00:59.633
I'm responsible for tearing off those fancy packages

00:00:59.700 --> 00:01:01.633
and present the truth to you.

00:01:01.700 --> 00:01:03.933
To make it easier for everyone to get what they need,

00:01:03.933 --> 00:01:07.033
I have divided the content of my channel into several series.

